
= SDL_AtomicGetPtr =
Use this function to get the value of a pointer atomically.


== Syntax ==
<syntaxhighlight lang='c++'>
void* SDL_AtomicGetPtr(void** a)
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''a'''
|a pointer to a pointer
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the current value of a pointer.

